  "body_html": "<!DOCTYPE html\n  SYSTEM \"about:legacy-compat\">\n<html lang=\"en-us\" dir=\"ltr\"><head><title>Environment</title><meta charset=\"utf-8\"><link rel=\"stylesheet\" type=\"text/css\" media=\"screen,projection\" href=\"/resource/css/style-v2.css\"><script type=\"text/javascript\" src=\"js/sap-strings.js\"></script></head><body class=\"en-us sap-light centered navigation-default enumeration-disabled\"><div id=\"d4h5-main-container\" class=\"container_12\" role=\"application\"><div id=\"d4h5-section-container\" class=\"grid_12\"><div id=\"d4h5-main-content\" class=\"grid_8 alpha omega\"><section><div class=\"page topic  - topic-topic \" id=\"loio7707da531198434de10000000a174cb4\"><h1 class=\"title topictitle1\">Environment</h1><div class=\"body\">\n<div class=\"section\"><section class=\"section\" type=\"Use\"><h2 class=\"section_title\">Use</h2>\n<p class=\"p\">In the upper application toolbar, under Environment, you will find the following functions:</p>\n</section></div>\n<div class=\"section\"><section class=\"section\" type=\"Structure\"><h2 class=\"section_title\">Structure</h2>\n<ul class=\"ul\"><li class=\"li\"><p class=\"p\"><a class=\"xref\" href=\"2419c55368511d4be10000000a174cb4.html\">Worklist</a></p></li><li class=\"li\"><p class=\"p\"><a class=\"xref\" href=\"3f14da531198434de10000000a174cb4.html\">Object Links</a> (links to the respective transaction)</p></li><li class=\"li\"><p class=\"p\"><a class=\"xref\" href=\"b707da531198434de10000000a174cb4.html\">Change Documents for the Transaction</a></p></li><li class=\"li\"><p class=\"p\"><a class=\"xref\" href=\"701ada531198434de10000000a174cb4.html\">Regulatory Reporting</a> (in money market trading)</p></li>\n<li class=\"li\"><p class=\"p\">Position indicator (for options market transactions). This takes you to the <a class=\"xref\" href=\"5a15da531198434de10000000a174cb4.html\">Futures Account Generic Position.</a></p></li></ul>\n</section></div>\n</div><div class=\"related-links\"> </div></div></section><div class=\"clear\"></div>\n</div></div></div></body></html>"
